<br />Thanks RetroRalph!  What I meant on the website is that the screen saver is completely decoupled from UberNES emulator; users still have to have the proper ROMs for movie emulation/playback but they do not need to use UberNES to download movies or do anything else.  The website text is a little confusing and should be changed.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

