	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />which is better to use, GDI or DirectDraw?
<br />
<br />UPDATE: When I use GDI for the graphics I only ever see games playing in my left monitor (identified by Windows as monitor "2" under the "Settings" tab) no matter what I set the movie tile width or game resolution to.  When I use DirectDraw everything works perfectly and I see games on both monitors.  DirectDraw also seems faster.  Just FYI.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


